snippet.title: Starbomb - Nintendo Online‚Äôs Greatest Announcement (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Music Video animated by ‚ñ∏ @Shigloo 
Pre-Order Merch ‚ñ∏ http://store.starbomb.com/
Pre-Save the album ‚ñ∏ https://stayleveldistro.com/BOOM
Listen to ‚ÄúNintendo Online‚Äôs Greatest Announcement" ‚ñ∏ https://stayleveldistro.com/nintendolisten
Instagram ‚ñ∏   https://www.instagram.com/starbombband  

LYRICS

Listen up girl, I know you a Nintendo fan
Got a Switch day one so you can hold it in your hand 
Sync that wifi, know you got that speedy broadband
So you can download retro games from US and Japan

But don‚Äôt tell no one I got the secrets straight from my dad 
And they‚Äôll get mad at my dad if they know he‚Äôs been bad 
So listen close and remember all the news that I got

For the retro game drop
That‚Äôs right for Nintendo Online‚Äôs drop
We got the game Squimble 2 it‚Äôs the sequel to Squimble 
Classic Mario and Zelda would just be too simple 
Ronnie‚Äôs Barnyard Tussle was an all time fave
And also Shave the Cat and Adventures of Dave

Pillow Fight Simulator really raised the bar
So far you haven‚Äôt experienced Banana Bazaar
Egg Maze, Gromplins, and Pachinko de Mayo
Mattel‚Äôs Barbie‚Äôs Adventures in Toledo, Ohio

And maybe you were thinkin‚Äô that these weren‚Äôt the best 
But just wait ‚Äòtil you see the rest
I said wait ‚Äòtil you see the rest
Of these games, go (chiptune sounds)

Grab your SD card 

Got Diarrhea Warrior, and also more of your
Favorite games like Cuck Hunt, and Mecha Lawyer 
Regular Sword, and Basketbunt ‚Äò89
The video game version of I Saw The Sign

We‚Äôre the luckiest gamers you‚Äôll be happy to learn 
That instead of Kirby‚Äôs Adventures we got Super Plerm 
That‚Äôs the Super Nintendo remake of a game called Plerm
It was a game for the classic NES called Plerm

If you‚Äôre expecting greatness you‚Äôve come to the right place
Cause instead of Galaga you‚Äôve got Shooty Gun Space 
Also Asteroid, no relation of course
Also Toad‚Äôs Alimony which I‚Äôll gladly endorse

Okay, to be honest there‚Äôs a game I‚Äôve been hypin‚Äô
It‚Äôs a Mario game, yeah, it‚Äôs Mario Teaches Wipin‚Äô 
That‚Äôs not all, bitch I haven‚Äôt even gotten even started 
‚ÄòCause tomorrow they‚Äôre releasing Smart Fella: He Felt Smarted

And if you think that ain‚Äôt enough to put your skills to the test
Wait ‚Äòtil you see the rest 
I said wait ‚Äòtil you see the rest
Of these games go (more chiptune sounds)

If I wasn‚Äôt clear before Super Plerm‚Äôs all we got
If classic Plerm was what you were hoping to play you sadly cannot
If you bought Nintendo Classic though you can try Plerm 
But that is only a demo for a limited term

Yoshi‚Äôs Tax Shelter is a game for the ages
The pages and pages of ‚Äòtorial that‚Äôre needed to play this 
Are made of a shade of a gray that you can‚Äôt even read though
And so then Yoshi goes to prison and dies

Russian Surrender, Super Financial Lender
Dinosaurs vs. Ducks, Postal Service Defender
Also Squark, and the remake of Squark
I recommend playing Squark right before you play Squark

There‚Äôs a lot of the plot that Squark just left out
So in order to understand just what Squark‚Äôs all about
I also recommend logging on to the wiki for Squark 
So you can get a real deep dive on Squark

If after all these games then you just aren‚Äôt impressed 
Sorry there‚Äôs no more left
I said sorry there‚Äôs no more left

(even more chiptune sounds)

Games go 

(still even more chiptune sounds)

snippet.title: Series 18, Episode 2 - '...and then a detective comes.' | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Jack Dee has a dramatic change of wardrobe and Rosie Jones presents her new baby.

------------


Follow the show at http://www.twitter.com/taskmaster
Become a fan at https://www.facebook.com/officialtaskmaster
Buy Taskmaster merch: https://taskmasterstore.com/

------------

In this Broadcast Award-winning, BAFTA and Emmy Award-nominated entertainment show, Taskmaster tyrant Greg Davies (Man Down, Cuckoo), with the help of his loyal assistant Alex Horne (The Horne Section and the show‚Äôs creator), sets out to test the wiles, wit and wisdom of five hyper-competitive comedians.

Comedians that have risked life, limb, and dignity in the hope of making the Taskmaster proud so far include: Frank Skinner (The Frank Skinner Show), Mel Giedroyc (The Great British Bake Off), Romesh Ranganathan (Asian Provocateur), Hugh Dennis (Outnumbered), Sally Phillips (Bridget Jones‚Äô Diary), Rose Matafeo (Edinburgh Comedy Award Winner 2018), and Russell Howard (The Russell Howard Hour). Unaware of what awaits them in each wax-sealed envelope, only one competitor can become the victorious owner of His Royal Task-ness‚Äô golden head and be crowned the next Taskmaster Champion.

snippet.title: Kentucky judge fatally shot by sheriff in courthouse
snippet.description:
A judge in a Kentucky town was shot and killed Thursday at the local courthouse and the local sheriff surrendered without incident.

Governor Andy Beshear posted that a district judge in Letcher County was killed, District Judge Kevin Mullins.

The judge was announced dead at the scene, with police saying that preliminary investigation indicates the local sheriff shot Mullins multiple times after an argument inside the courthouse.

P1Harmony, releasing 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô on September 20th.
‚ÄúStill, I overcome‚Äù title track ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô, P1Hamony‚Äôs unique way to overcome loneliness
‚ÄòGlobal Sensation‚Äô P1Harmony is being a solid ground to listeners with 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô

P1Harmony, seeking change against established norms, has achieved true harmony between the +WORLD (meta-verse world) and the REAL WORLD (real world) through their DISHARMONY and HARMONY series. After entering the Billboard Main chart and performing on a large-scale world tour, P1Harmony made their name as the chosen HERO (NEW KIDS) through 7th Mini Album.

The title track of the 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô is about emptiness and loneliness that came to P1Harmony, who became a HERO after saving the world and restoring peace. Going beyond the conventional perception of a hero as a solely grand figure, HERO, reinterpreted through P1Harmony‚Äôs unique perspective, conveys the power to overcome the universal emotion of sadness through dance and music.

This album's title 'SAD SONG' features a total of seven tracks, including the title track of the same name, along with other songs like the pop track 'It‚Äôs Alright,' which has an impressive reggae rhythm with electric guitar sounds, the energizing 'Last Call,' which brings vitality to the never-ending heat, the hopeful 'Welcome To,' encouraging the start of a new chapter, the medium-tempo track 'All You,' which is a confession of eternal love, the unit song 'WASP' by INTAK and JONGSEOB, which marks their first attempt at a unit track in P1Harmony, and even an English version of the title track 'SAD SONG.'

P1Harmony, who has been steadily building their musical capabilities by actively participating in their previous projects, put a lot of effort into this 7th Mini Album 'SAD SONG' as well. KEEHO was deeply involved in, from the concept planning stage of the album, and even contributed to the composition of 'It‚Äôs Alright.' INTAK and JONGSEOB participated in writing lyrics and composing the unit track 'WASP,' as well as writing lyrics for all the tracks on this album. JIUNG also contributed to the production of six tracks, enhancing this album's overall quality.

P1Harmony continues to build their original musical world with 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô, which contains various musical experiments. Listeners will be able to enjoy the positive energy that will overcome any adversity, as well as solid music that is produced with P1Harmony‚Äôs individuality and skills

P1Harmony, seeking change against established norms, has achieved true harmony between the +WORLD (meta-verse world) and the REAL WORLD (real world) through their DISHARMONY and HARMONY series. After entering the Billboard Main chart and performing on a large-scale world tour, P1Harmony made their name as the chosen HERO (NEW KIDS) through 7th Mini Album.

The title track of the 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô is about emptiness and loneliness that came to P1Harmony, who became a HERO after saving the world and restoring peace. Going beyond the conventional perception of a hero as a solely grand figure, HERO, reinterpreted through P1Harmony‚Äôs unique perspective, conveys the power to overcome the universal emotion of sadness through dance and music.

This album's title 'SAD SONG' features a total of seven tracks, including the title track of the same name, along with other songs like the pop track 'It‚Äôs Alright,' which has an impressive reggae rhythm with electric guitar sounds, the energizing 'Last Call,' which brings vitality to the never-ending heat, the hopeful 'Welcome To,' encouraging the start of a new chapter, the medium-tempo track 'All You,' which is a confession of eternal love, the unit song 'WASP' by INTAK and JONGSEOB, which marks their first attempt at a unit track in P1Harmony, and even an English version of the title track 'SAD SONG.'

P1Harmony, who has been steadily building their musical capabilities by actively participating in their previous projects, put a lot of effort into this 7th Mini Album 'SAD SONG' as well. KEEHO was deeply involved in, from the concept planning stage of the album, and even contributed to the composition of 'It‚Äôs Alright.' INTAK and JONGSEOB participated in writing lyrics and composing the unit track 'WASP,' as well as writing lyrics for all the tracks on this album. JIUNG also contributed to the production of six tracks, enhancing this album's overall quality.

P1Harmony continues to build their original musical world with 7th Mini Album ‚ÄòSAD SONG‚Äô, which contains various musical experiments. Listeners will be able to enjoy the positive energy that will overcome any adversity, as well as solid music that is produced with P1Harmony‚Äôs individuality and skills

snippet.title: NEW in 2025 - Siren's Curse!
snippet.description:
The Roller Coaster Capital of the World¬Æ will add fathoms of thrills to its world-renowned and record-breaking collection of scream machines with the 2025 debut of Siren‚Äôs Curse ‚Äì the tallest, fastest and longest ‚Äútilt‚Äù roller coaster in North America. 

Siren‚Äôs Curse hearkens to the legend and lore of mysterious creatures living beneath the surface of Lake Erie; often spoken of ‚Äì but never spotted. The sirens of the lake who lured sailors to their underwater demise with their sweet, seductive songs will finally rise to land and attempt to entrap guests in a sinister two-minute fate of non-stop roller coaster innovation.

Riders will hear the echo of the siren‚Äôs chilling melodies as they ascend an old 160-foot-tall Lake Erie shipping crane tower, the sounds growing more sinister as riders reach the top. Their fate will hang in the balance as they encounter the roller coaster‚Äôs signature moment: a dead stop on a ‚Äúbroken off‚Äù section of track. The creaking platform holding the train of riders will slowly tilt the entire train into a 90-degree vertical position, forcing riders to peer straight down with the hope their train will connect to the twisted track below.

As the track locks into place, riders will flee from the beckoning call of the siren and plunge into the abyss, speeding through 2,966 feet of track at a top speed of 58 mph. The ride will feature 13 weightless airtime moments, two 360-degree, zero-gravity barrel rolls and a high-speed ‚Äútriple-down‚Äù element with twisted and overbanked track.

snippet.title: Devin Haney Speaks Out On Ryan Garcia Fight, Floyd Mayweather, Career Journey | THE ART OF WARD
snippet.description:
THE ART OF WARD is BACK! On the latest episode, boxing superstar Devin Haney speaks out in an exclusive interview with Andre Ward‚ÄîHaney‚Äôs first since his controversial no decision against Ryan Garcia in April. Haney reflects on the negotiating process, the red flags leading up to fight night, what happened in the ring and finding our Ryan tested positive for PEDs after. 

Plus, Haney looks back on his career journey to this point, including leaving Top Rank, fights vs. George Kambosos Jr., and controversial decision victory over Vasiliy Lomachenko. He also discusses his relationship with his father, dealing with pressure, and Floyd's impact on him. 

#allthesmoke #MMA #boxing #AllTheSmokeFight #DevinHaney #haneygarcia #ryangarcia #eddiehearn #andreward #floydmayweather

snippet.title: Wreckage Of Titan Submersible Reveal How It Imploded
snippet.description:
The US Coast Guard has just begun its public inquiry into the Titan Submersible accident, and in the process has released a number of documents, including, critically footage from a remotely operated vehicle showing the wreckages on the ocean floor.
I believe this wreckage confirms that the failure began at the interface between the carbon fiber pressure hull and the forward titanium interface ring. A great deal of composite debris has been pushed backwards into the rear hemisphere, while almost none is visible near the forward sphere.

Many more documents are available here and more witnesses will testify over coming days, providing new insights into this event
https://www.news.uscg.mil/News-by-Region/Headquarters/Titan-Submersible/

Follow me on Twitter for more updates:
https://twitter.com/DJSnM

https://discord.gg/zStmKbM

snippet.title: Introducing the PlayStation 30th Anniversary Collection
snippet.description:
Celebrating 30 years of gaming, the PlayStation 30th Anniversary Collection utilizes the original PlayStation color design and integrates it into the latest line of PS5 hardware products.
 
The collection includes:
PlayStation 5 Digital Edition ‚Äì 30th Anniversary Limited Edition Bundle
Includes: Limited Edition PS5 Digital Edition console and matching accessories ‚Äì DualSense wireless controller, Console Cover for Disc Drive (Disc Drive sold separately), vertical stand, poster (1 of 30 possible designs), original PlayStation-style cable connector housing, four PlayStation Shapes cable ties, PlayStation sticker and paperclip.
 
PlayStation 5 Pro ‚Äì 30th Anniversary Limited Edition Bundle
Includes: Limited Edition PS5 Pro console and matching accessories ‚Äì DualSense Edge wireless controller, DualSense Charging Station, and all items included in the PS5 Digital Edition Bundle.
 
PlayStation Portal Remote Player ‚Äì 30th Anniversary Limited Edition (standalone)
DualSense Edge Wireless Controller ‚Äì 30th Anniversary Limited Edition (standalone)
DualSense Wireless Controller ‚Äì 30th Anniversary Limited Edition (standalone)
 
See PlayStation Blog for details. While supplies last: https://blog.playstation.com/2024/09/19/celebrating-30-years-of-playstation-with-a-nostalgic-look/

#ps5 #playstation

snippet.title: NHL 25 Official Franchise Trailer | Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Pre-order the NHL 25 Deluxe Edition now & start playing 7 days early! http://x.ea.com/81339

Franchise Mode gets a revamp in NHL 25. Starting with the Franchise hub, streamlined navigation gives players access to new, relevant, and easy-to-digest information, like box scores, player stats, an award tracker, an updated league ticker, and a goals and challenges display. 

Plus, you can now ask players to change their playstyle, which can lead to positive or negative effects, and set player goals. In an update to Chel‚Äôs contract offer overlay and Collective Bargaining Agreement, support for No Trade and No Movement clauses is now available for each contract year, with NTC and NMC icons that make it easy to keep track of each. New conversation functions enhance negotiations, making promises, waivers, and counters a faster, more intuitive process.

Subscribe on YouTube for more NHL 25 Trailers: https://bit.ly/3kF5rTK

Follow for official news  
TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@easportsnhl
Instagram: https://instagram.com/easportsnhl 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/easportsnhl

snippet.title: DOG MAN | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Dog Man - In Theaters January 31

Part dog, part man, all hero. 

From DreamWorks Animation‚Äîcreators of the beloved blockbuster franchises Kung Fu Panda, How to Train Your Dragon and The Boss Baby‚Äîcomes the canine-crime-fighting film adaptation of Dav Pilkey‚Äôs New York Times bestselling literary phenomenon: Dog Man. 

When a faithful police dog and his human police officer owner are injured together on the job, a harebrained but life-saving surgery fuses the two of them together and Dog Man is born. Dog Man is sworn to protect and serve‚Äîand fetch, sit and roll over.  

As Dog Man embraces his new identity and strives to impress his Chief (Lil Rel Howery, Get Out, Free Guy), he must stop the pretty evil plots of feline supervillain Petey the Cat (Pete Davidson; Saturday Night Live, The King of Staten Island). Petey‚Äôs latest plan is to clone himself, creating the kitten Lil Petey, to double his ability to do crime stuff. Things get complicated, though, when Lil Petey forges an unexpected bond with Dog Man. 

When Lil Petey falls into the clutches of a common enemy, Dog Man and Petey reluctantly join forces in an action-packed race against time to rescue the young kitten. In the process, they discover the power of family (and kittens!) to bring even the most hostile foes together.  

Dog Man also stars Isla Fisher (Wedding Crashers, Rango) as TV reporter Sarah Hatoff; Poppy Liu (Hacks, The Afterparty) as Petey‚Äôs assistant, Butler; Emmy nominee Stephen Root (Barry, King of the Hill) as Grampa; Billy Boyd (the Lord of the Rings franchise, Seed of Chucky) as Sarah‚Äôs cameraman, Seamus; and Emmy and Golden Globe winner Ricky Gervais (The Office, Extras) as Flippy the fish.  

Dog Man is directed by Emmy winner Peter Hastings (The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants, Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness), whose credits include the groundbreaking animated series Animaniacs and Pinky and the Brain. The film is produced by Karen Foster (Spirit Untamed), who served as co-producer on DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs How to Train Your Dragon. 

Launched in 2016 by Dav Pilkey‚Äîthe #1 global bestselling author and award-winning illustrator of the Captain Underpants books‚Äîthe Dog Man Scholastic series now includes 12 books. The series has more than 60 million copies in print and has been translated into 47 languages. Cat Kid Comic Club, a spin-off of Dog Man launched in 2020, has also topped bestseller lists around the world. The most recent Dog Man book, Dog Man: Twenty Thousand Fleas Under the Sea, was overall the #1 bestselling children‚Äôs book in the U.S. in 2023, across all children‚Äôs formats and ages. Pilkey‚Äôs newest book in the Dog Man Series, Dog Man: Big Jim Begins, is set to release on December 3, 2024.

DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs Dog Man will be distributed by Universal Pictures.

snippet.title: 3 Tips for VA Disability Claims | Common Misconceptions with VA Disability Claims | theSITREP
snippet.description:
In this episode of theSITREP, Paul covers three tips to consider when submitting a claim for VA disability.  For additional information and to see which benefits you or your family may qualify, visit the web links below.

To view all our content, visit http://www.youtube.com/@VAmadesimple

To view or listen to podcasts, visit https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2quV7hnnZ3nfmHYbnpovNyv_LPfc6OuT

Need an immediate answer or help with a situation regarding VA benefits? Call, 24/7, at 1-800-MyVA411 (698-2411)

Have a topic suggestion or question you would like to see addressed on a future episode of theSITREP? Email us at theSITREP@va.gov.  Please know that VA policy precludes us from being able to respond to personal email, however our team does its best to review and consider each submission.  Thank you in advance for contacting us and supporting theSITREP!

Want to receive the newest episodes of theSITREP in your email inbox? Sign up for the VetResources email newsletter, which features the newest episodes and also offers Veteran-centric news stories, various deals and discounts, employment opportunities, and much more. To sign up, visit https://news.va.gov/vetresources/

ADDITIONAL INFORMATION

To submit a claim for VA disability, visit:
https://www.va.gov/disability/how-to-file-claim/

To submit an Intent to File, visit:
https://www.va.gov/resources/your-intent-to-file-a-va-claim/

To find a VA-accredited Veteran Service Officer, visit:
https://www.va.gov/get-help-from-accredited-representative/find-rep/

To find presumptive condition information, visit and scroll down to your era of service:
https://www.va.gov/resources/the-pact-act-and-your-va-benefits/

ABOUT VA
The Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) is comprised of three different administrations:

(1) Veterans Health Administration (VHA) - Provides health care at 1,298 facilities, including 171 hospitals and 1,113 outpatient clinics, serving 9 million enrolled Veterans each year.

(2) Veterans Benefits Administration (VBA) - Provides a variety of benefits and services for Service Members, Veterans, and their families including compensation, pension and fiduciary, insurance, education, loan guaranty, vocational rehabilitation and employment, and more.

(3) National Cemetery Administration (NCA) - Provides burial space for Veterans and their eligible family members, and maintains national cemeteries as national shrines, sacred to the honor and memory of those interred or memorialized there.

DISCLAIMER: The Department of Veterans Affairs does not endorse or officially sanction any entities that may be discussed in this video, nor any media, products, or services they may provide.

This video was produced and published by VA New England Healthcare System.

#theSITREP  #VetResources #disabledveteran

snippet.title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What's it feel like to die? From director Bong Joon Ho, comes Mickey 17 - only in theaters January 31, 2025. #Mickey17  

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the job‚Ä¶ to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, ‚ÄúMickey 17‚Äù stars Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúTenet‚Äù), Naomi Ackie (‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù), Steven Yeun (‚ÄúNope‚Äù), with Academy Award nominees Toni Collette (‚ÄúHereditary‚Äù), and Mark Ruffalo (‚ÄúPoor Things‚Äù). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner (Oscar winner for ‚ÄúMoonlight,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù), Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winner for ‚ÄúMoonlight,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù ‚ÄúSnowpiercer‚Äù). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúBardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúThe Favourite,‚Äù ‚ÄúCruella‚Äù). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,‚Äù ‚ÄúFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw‚Äù). The costume designer is Catherine George (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù Snowpiercer‚Äù). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on January 31, 2025, and internationally beginning on 28 January 2025.

snippet.title: iPhone 16 Pro review: only one reason to upgrade
snippet.description:
The new iPhone 16 Pro is a minor improvement over the 15 Pro, but a new camera setting makes for much better photos. Almost all of its highlight features will arrive in future software updates, like the new Apple Intelligence AI features the company says will start slowly arriving in October. All that said, the iPhone 16 Pro does contain one extremely notable camera update, and it‚Äôs a good one ‚Äî although it‚Äôs probably not what you think. #Apple #iPhone16 #Technology

snippet.title: Canelo vs Berlanga FIGHT HIGHLIGHTS: September 14, 2024 | PBC PPV on Prime Video
snippet.description:
Mexican superstar and pound-for-pound great Canelo √Ålvarez delivered another virtuoso performance by dropping the previously unbeaten Edgar Berlanga on his way to defending his unified WBC, WBA and WBO Super Middleweight World Championships via unanimous decision as Canelo Promotions presented a Mexican Independence Day Weekend extravaganza headlining a PBC Pay-Per-View available on Prime Video Saturday night from T-Mobile Arena in Las Vegas.
 
"I did good. Now what are they gonna say? They said I don't fight young fighters. They always talk, but I'm the best fighter in the world,‚Äù said Canelo.
 
In the latest edition of the historic boxing rivalry between Mexico and Puerto Rico, Canelo (62-2-2, 39 KOs) sent his legion of fans into a frenzy early as he connected on a perfect left hook midway through round three that sent Berlanga (22-1, 17 KOs) to the mat. Berlanga was able to make it through the round and tried to impose his physicality on Canelo, with the two getting tied up, trading low blows and nearly hitting the canvas in a tense moment during round five.
 
"I got a little angry with his tactics, but I'm Mexican man,‚Äù said Canelo. ‚ÄúIt means a lot to fight on this day. It's an honor to represent my country on this day.‚Äù
 
"I'm upset because at the end of the day I'm a winner,‚Äù said Berlanga. ‚ÄúI fought a legend tonight and did my best to represent Puerto Rico. We're fighters and we try to throw our opponent off their game. I took his best shot and I knew I could take his punches and return them. I could have jabbed a lot more, but I was in there with a legend.‚Äù
 
Using the ring generalship that‚Äôs made him a future Hall of Famer, Canelo continued to control the action, turning up the heat in the later rounds, landing 16 power shots in round eight and 20 in round ten, according to CompuBox. The punch stats reflected Canelo‚Äôs dominance throughout the 12 rounds, as he out landed Berlanga 201 to 119.
 
"My experience and my talent was the difference,‚Äù said Canelo. ‚ÄúIt's about hard work and intelligence. It's everything together. If you have talent, you need discipline as well.‚Äù
 
Berlanga remained game throughout, continuing to throw punches and look for openings, even as Canelo broke him down with his varied attack. In the end, Canelo‚Äôs 49% connect rate on power punches buoyed him to victory by scores of 118-109 twice and 117-110.
 
"A lot of people say we can't, but we can,‚Äù said Canelo ‚ÄúLas Vegas is like a second home for Mexicans. We are warriors and we never give up. I‚Äôm going to rest and then I'm going to decide what's next."

#CaneloBerlanga #Canelo #Berlanga

snippet.description:

Borderlands was a pillar in the looter/shooter genre, and a younger Lemon spent hours upon hours blasting enemies into bits with hundreds of different weapons. 
But what if we couldn't? What if you had to kill every single enemy in only 1 shot? 
Could you? Is that even possible?

...oh, you're asking me? I dunno, I just work here.
Can you beat Borderlands 1 with only 1 shots?

snippet.title: Why Louisiana's $1.3 Billion Shrimp Industry Could Go Extinct | Big Business | Business Insider
snippet.description:
Louisiana catches about 70 million tons of shrimp, but it's not enough to meet America's surging demand. Cheap imports make up 90% of what the US consumes, and most of it is farmed in countries like India using controversial tactics. Dock prices in Louisiana have fallen to compete. It's left US shrimpers with a perfect storm of rock-bottom prices and sky-high fuel. Up and down the supply chain, companies worry this may be the last generation of Louisiana shrimpers.

snippet.title: Minecraft: GUESS THE BUILD! (Unlikely Pairings)
snippet.description:
Today we are playing a building minigame (with Jimmy, Impulse, Gem, Skizz and Joel) where we build something, the next person guesses that build and we build someone elses guess in a cycle until we have swapped 3 times.. and we see what the build looks like. snippet.title: What Happened To Our New Catamaran?
snippet.description:
We‚Äôre in Cebu, Philippines at the HH Catamarans factory for our first round of warranty repairs.¬† Sadly, things didn‚Äôt go as expected.
https://www.gonewiththewynns.com
‚òùBehind the Scenes, Gear Guides & More

‚õµOur Catamaran
https://www.gonewiththewynns.com/curiosity-sailboat

üì∑ Photo & Video Gear üì∑
https://www.gonewiththewynns.com/photo-video-gear 

üì±Socials   
INSTAGRAM: https://instagram.com/the_wynns/ 
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/GoneWithTheWynns 

üìßEMAIL notifications, so you never miss a videoüç¶
http://bit.ly/gwtw-social

üé∂ MUSIC for vids. 
2 Months Free:  https://bit.ly/artlist-GWTW

üé® Creative Assets for Vids (SFX, Templates & Presets): 
 - https://bit.ly/motion-array-GWTW 

üéΩGET YOUR SWAG ON:  https://gonewiththewynns.teemill.com/


_____________________________
The boat wasn‚Äôt in great shape, many of the jobs didn‚Äôt get done, and not all the work done was up to spec.

This is a new factory for HH, and CURIOSITY is the first finished boat they have worked on.¬† So, it was a bit painful and it took far longer than expected.  Let's just say it was a series of unfortunate events for all of us.

As you can imagine, everyone at HH feels TERRIBLE about the whole situation.¬† They have assured us that they stand behind their product and their customers.¬†

The Cebu factory now has new management, new systems in place, additional experts, new training programs and has undergone infrastructure changes. ¬†Just before we left, we were able to meet Rudy, the new general manager. ¬†He is an impressive fellow with 24 years in design and manufacturing in the marine, automotive, aerospace and defense industries. He shared some of his grand plans for the Cebu factory and I do believe him when he says all future work will be up to the high standards HH is known for.

So, while it has been a very stressful and expensive five plus weeks of living out of hotels.¬† We are happy to be back in our home and preparing for our next big passage.  Plus, we get to share the journey with some of you, our Curiosity Crew!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WE‚ÄôRE JASON AND NIKKI WYNN.  A couple of explorers, modern-day documentarians, and cultivators of curiosity.

We‚Äôve been chasing our curiosity around the world on wheels and keels since 2011. Why?  Because curiosity is the key to unlocking life.  It pushes us outside our comfort zone, softens our assumptions, and helps us embrace the great unknown.  The more we let our curiosity lead the way, the more we discover about ourselves and the world around us.

Things We're Most Curious About...

GETTING OFF-GRID 
Our home is also our transportation and we spend weeks away from civilization and sometimes land.  So self-reliance and sustainable living are a must.  We've learned heaps about renewable energy, managing waste, creating safe drinking water and foraging for food.  We carefully manage our resources and we‚Äôre always looking for new and better ways to do so.  

TALKING TO STRANGERS
People are busy (even on remote islands) and travelers are a dime a dozen.  It takes time to talk to strangers, and even more time to have a real connection.  Going the extra mile to get to know someone is a commitment. 

Which is why these are our most treasured experiences.  Setting off into the world with curiosity as our guide and nature as our compass.  We talk to strangers and accept hospitality without fear or reservations.  Both giving and receiving.

ALTERNATIVE LIVING
These are people who are doing things differently. Forgoing the mainstream, seeking freedom and living on the margins. Creative, unique and inspiring people who challenge our ideas of home and community.

Our journey is ever-evolving but the mission remains the same: #CultivateCuriosity

snippet.title: Doors Floor Two: The Mines (5 Players Not Recommended)
